    The VOI snapshot contains ODDS and sales information for each  
    Voittaja event.
    
    The information displayed includes:
 
    game index    - Voittaja game index (1-6)
    dates         - current date and dates when sales are opened for 
                    the event
    event name    - voittaja event name   
    event code    - voittaja draw number
    game          - game status for the draw (open,closed)
    row           - number of each row
    name          - participants name associated with row number
    odds          - odds on outcome predicted 
    amount        - amount bet on each row 
    sts           - status of each row
    total pool    - total pool for the entire event
    tax           - amount of tax due
    round pool    - n/a

