    net pool      - 70% of total sales.

    Fields Shown Only When The Event Is Final.

    results 1     - Outcome of the event.  Multiple winners are shown in 
                    convention: Results 1, 2, 3, etc
    row           - Winning row number 
    winner        - Participant name associated with row number
    amount bet    - Total amount bet on winning row
    odds          - odds used for the payouts calculation
    cancelled rows- cancelled rows numbers 
    beginning     - date when the sales were opened
    sales




